        "timestamp": "2019-12-04 10:41:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Guys,\n\nI've addressed all comments, that is:\n* heat templates have been renamed to match format from CDS (e.g. firewall -> vfw)\n* Corrected service names to be more meaningful\n* Didn't include vf-module information in resource label as k8splugin does it automaticaly\n* Removed ssh key-based access as I've had issues with running it properly (by extracting ssh-pub-key from secrets). Password authentication is the only access method to VM slaves now (just like in old k8s-vFW)\n\nIf you're fine with it, we can get it merged.",
        "patchset_number": 3
      },
